OL,3,CWhat is a 'council of sanctuary' and
OL,4,Cwhat does it mean?
OL,6,FLocal authorities across the UK have
OL,7,Fbecome 'councils of sanctuary', in
OL,8,Fplaces like Newcastle, Manchester,
OL,9,FOxfordshire and Perth and Kinross.
OL,11,FCumberland Council's recent plans to
OL,12,Fapply for the status prompted both pro-
OL,13,F and anti-immigration protests, and
OL,14,Fcouncil meetings on the topic have
OL,15,Fseen packed public galleries.
OL,17,FBut what is a council of sanctuary,
OL,18,Fand what would it mean for those
OL,19,Fliving within its borders?
OL,21,FWhat is a council of sanctuary?
