OL,3,CWhat is a 'council of sanctuary' and
OL,4,Cwhat does it mean?
OL,6,FWhat does being a council of sanctuary
OL,7,Finvolve?
OL,9,FSanctuary status involves establishing
OL,10,Fa framework to ensure that a welcoming
OL,11,Fand inclusive environment for people
OL,12,Fseeking sanctuary is created within
OL,13,Fcouncil institutions, local
OL,14,Fcommunities, and wider organisations
OL,15,Flike schools and universities.
OL,17,FCouncils seeking sanctuary status
OL,18,Fshould engage with local City of
OL,19,FSanctuary groups, if they exist, and
OL,20,Fhear from local refugee groups and
OL,21,Fpeople "with lived experience".
