OL,3,CWhat is a 'council of sanctuary' and
OL,4,Cwhat does it mean?
OL,6,FThe council would be expected to
OL,7,Fdevelop a strategy for supporting
OL,8,Fpeople seeking sanctuary, which would
OL,9,Fbe embedded across council services.
OL,11,FTo join the City of Sanctuary Local
OL,12,FAuthority Network, councils would have
OL,13,Fto support its vision and endorse its
OL,14,Fcharter.
OL,16,FDoes sanctuary status affect the
OL,17,Fnumber of asylum seekers in a council
OL,18,Farea?
