OL,3,CWhat is a 'council of sanctuary' and
OL,4,Cwhat does it mean?
OL,6,FThe number of asylum seekers, and
OL,7,Fwhere they are placed to live, is
OL,8,Fdetermined by the UK Government.
OL,9,FStatus as a council of sanctuary
OL,10,Fshould therefore not affect decisions
OL,11,Fon asylum applications, dispersal
OL,12,Fareas, or housing strategies.
OL,14,FWho is affected by council of
OL,15,Fsanctuary status?
OL,17,FThe City of Sanctuary Local Authority
OL,18,FNetwork points out that local
OL,19,Fauthorities have a duty to "support
OL,20,Fall people in need, without exception."
