OL,3,CWhat is a 'council of sanctuary' and
OL,4,Cwhat does it mean?
OL,6,FThis responsibility is set out under
OL,7,Fthe Care Act, the Children Act, the
OL,8,FEqualities Act, and housing and
OL,9,Fhomelessness legislation, "to ensure
OL,10,Fthat everyone, regardless of
OL,11,Fbackground, is treated fairly and with
OL,12,Fdignity."
OL,14,FManchester City Council, which was
OL,15,Fawarded council of sanctuary status in
OL,16,FOctober 2024, says it "uses the term
OL,17,F'people seeking sanctuary' to focus on
OL,18,Findividuals, not immigration status."
