OL,3,CWhat is a 'council of sanctuary' and
OL,4,Cwhat does it mean?
OL,6,FThe UK Government provides funding for
OL,7,Fseveral programmes for those seeking
OL,8,Fasylum, sometimes using the foreign
OL,9,Faid budget to support those fleeing
OL,10,Finternational crises.
OL,12,FThe City of Sanctuary Local Authority
OL,13,FNetwork says that working towards a
OL,14,Fcouncil of sanctuary status can often
OL,15,Flead to councils finding efficiencies
OL,16,Fand unlocking additional funding
OL,17,Fstreams. Effective planning and
OL,18,Fstrategies should also mean existing
OL,19,Fresources are used more effectively.
